    Title: Young India
    Editor: M. K. Gandhi
    Locus:
      Date: 15 August 1927
---
Mankind is notoriously too dense to read the signs that God sends from time
to time. We require drums to be beaten into our ears, before we would wake
from our trance and hear the warning and see that to lose oneself in all
is the only way to find oneself.
